page_title: 'Customize a model with Azure OpenAI Service and the Python SDK'
page_description: Learn how to create your own customized model with Azure OpenAI Service by using the Python SDK.
chunk_content: List fine-tuning eventsTo examine the individual fine-tuning events that were generated during training:# OpenAI Python 1.xYou may need to upgrade your OpenAI client library to the latest version with `pip install openai --upgrade` to run this command.```pythonresponse = client.fine_tuning.jobs.list_events(fine_tuning_job_id=job_id, limit=10)print(response.model_dump_json(indent=2))```# OpenAI Python 0.28.1This command isn't available in the 0.28.1 OpenAI Python library. Upgrade to the latest release.---
